      <div class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">🔧</span><span>OEM LG Parts</span></div>
      <div class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">🛡️</span><span>90-Day Warranty</span></div>
      <div class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">💰</span><span>$89 Diagnostic</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="brand-warranty-alert">
    <div class="brand-warranty-alert-inner">
      <div class="warranty-alert-icon">⚠️</div>
      <div class="warranty-alert-content">
        <h2>LG Linear Compressor — Your Unit May Be Covered at No Parts Cost</h2>
        <p>Following the <strong>Rosen v. LG Electronics class action settlement</strong>, LG extended its Inverter Linear Compressor warranty to <strong>10 years (parts and labor)</strong> for refrigerators manufactured 2014–2022. Covered series: LFXS, LFXC, LMXS, LMXC, LRMVS, LRMVC, LSXS, LSXC, LTCS, LRTLS.</p>
        <p>If your LG refrigerator isn't cooling and is in the 5-10 year range — <strong>don't pay for a compressor before you check your coverage.</strong> We verify this on every LG refrigerator compressor call before quoting anything. Call us with your model number and we'll check on the spot.</p>
        <div class="warranty-phones">
          <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn-primary">LA: {phone_la}</a>
          <a href="tel:+12134019019" class="btn-primary">OC: {phone_oc}</a>
          <a href="tel:+14242080228" class="btn-primary">Ventura: {phone_ventura}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="brand-intro">
    <div class="brand-intro-inner">
      <h2>LG Appliance Repair in Southern California</h2>
      <p>LG is one of the most popular appliance brands in Southern California — the brand has been a top seller for over a decade, and its French door refrigerators, front-load washers, and ranges are in hundreds of thousands of homes across LA, OC, and Ventura County. Our technicians service LG appliances daily and are familiar with every characteristic failure pattern the brand has developed over the years.</p>
      <p>The most significant issue facing LG refrigerator owners right now is the linear compressor — a design that was marketed as more efficient and longer-lasting, but has shown higher-than-expected failure rates at the 4-8 year mark. The class action settlement means many affected units are still covered under warranty. We always check before we quote a compressor job.</p>
      <p>Beyond the compressor issue, LG appliances are generally reliable when maintained. The most common calls we handle are LG washer OE drain errors (almost always a clogged filter, no parts needed), LG dryer vent restriction warnings, and LG dishwasher AE leak codes. Most of these resolve same visit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="brand-appliances">
    <div class="brand-appliances-inner">
      <h2>LG Appliances We Repair</h2>
      <div class="brand-appliance-grid">
        {appliances.map(a => (
          <div class="brand-appliance-card">
            <div class="appliance-header">
              <span class="appliance-icon">{a.icon}</span>
              <h3>{a.name}</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="failure-list">
