          <div class="review-author">— Sandra K., Burbank</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          <p>"LG dryer d90 error — they came out, cleared the vent, explained the restriction warning system. No parts needed. Also mentioned the thermal fuse was showing stress and replaced it proactively. That's the kind of service that prevents the next call."</p>
          <div class="review-author">— Patricia L., Thousand Oaks</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          <p>"LG dishwasher AE error — leak detected. Door gasket replaced same day. Technician found the sump filter was also completely clogged and cleared that at no extra charge. One visit, done right."</p>
          <div class="review-author">— James T., Newport Beach</div>
        </div>
      </div>
